Guild Chat Lines

There are three guild chat lines, the druid, heirophant,
and gaea lines.  The druid line is heard by all druids, 
The gaea line is heard by both druids and garou, while the
heirophant line is heard only by those of GL 28 and up.

dchat, edchat - Talk or emote on the druid line.
hd, ehd - Talk or emote on the heirophant line.
gaea, egaea - Talk or emote on the Gaea line.
